title: My 10 Scans - September 2016 (gnv64)
description:
After a long time, I am uploading a collection of my own scans. 
This collection contains 9 books, 1 magazine & a book sample.
All the books have OCR, bookmarks & covers with internal links from TOC.
Enjoy reading, do comment & seed for others:

01. A World of Nuclear Powers by Alastair Buchan (1969)
02. Devlok with Devdutt Pattanaik by Devdutt Pattanaik (2016)
03. My Life, My Rules - Stories of 18 Unconventional Careers by Sonia Golani (2012)
04. My Little India by Manoj Das (2003)
05. Shorty Gomes - Vintage Crime Stories Featuring Shorty Gomes, Bombay's Ace Private Eye by Ahmed Bunglowala (1993)
06. Smashing Physics - Inside the Discovery of the Higgs Boson by Jon Butterworth (2014)
07. SPAN - September/October 2016 on US Elections 2016 (magazine)
08. Survival of the Sickest by Dr. Sharon Moalem (2007)
09. The Scientific Edge by Jayant V. Narlikar (2003)
10. When...Questions to 50 Interesting Answers by Bal Phondke (2009)
11. Drop Dead - A Niki Marwah Mystery by Swati Kaushal (2012)(sample)
